<div
  style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eaeaea; border-radius: 8px;">
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px;">
    <h1 style="color: #111; font-weight: 900; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px;">Geenah's<br /><span
        style="-webkit-text-stroke: 1px #111; color: transparent;">Stitches</span></h1>
  </div>
  <h2 style="color: #111; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px;">Welcome, {{name}}! 🎉</h2>
  <p style="color: #444; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">Hi {{name}},</p>
  <p style="color: #444; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">
    Thank you for joining <strong>Geenah's Stitches</strong>! We're so excited to have you as part of our community.
  </p>
  <p style="color: #444; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">
    Explore our curated collection of beautifully crafted pieces, designed with love and attention to detail. Whether
    you're looking for something unique or a timeless classic, we've got you covered.
  </p>
  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
    <a href="{{storeUrl}}"
      style="background-color: #000; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">
      Browse Our Collection
    </a>
  </div>
  <p style="color: #444; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;">
    Need help? Simply reply to this email — we're always happy to assist.
  </p>
  <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea; margin: 32px 0;">
  <p style="color: #888; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;">
    &copy; {{year}} Geenah's Stitches. All rights reserved.
  </p>
</div>